=Transform this concept into a production-ready storyboard.

Avatar Video Duration (Seconds): {{ $json.avatar_duration }}

## CONCEPT INFO
- **Index:** {{ $('Loop Through Concepts').item.json.concept_number }}
- **Type:** {{ $('Loop Through Concepts').item.json.concept_type }}
- **Title:** {{ $('Loop Through Concepts').item.json.title }}

## FULL SCRIPT
{{ $('Loop Through Concepts').item.json.full_script }}

## CURRENT STORYBOARD
{{ JSON.stringify($('Loop Through Concepts').item.json.storyboard, null, 2) }}

## AVAILABLE SCREEN SHARE B-ROLL
These are screen recording clips from actual software demos. Use with broll_type: "screen".
{{ JSON.stringify($('Extract Snippets').item.json.broll_clips, null, 2) }}

## AVAILABLE AI-GENERATED B-ROLL
These are cinematic AI-generated clips for visual impact. 
Use with broll_type: "ai_generated" and specify ai_broll_index (0, 1, or 2).

{{ JSON.stringify($('Aggregate Flash B-Roll').item.json.flash_broll_generated.filter(item => item.status === 'succeeded'), null, 2) }}

**AI B-ROLL RULES:**
- **⚠️ CRITICAL: Any beat using AI B-roll MUST have the same duration_seconds
- Use ai_broll_index: 0, 1, or 2 to select which clip
- Best for: hook_reveal, body_flash, or high-impact transitions
- DO NOT overlap with screen B-roll - choose one type per beat

## TIMING

- Total:  {{ $('Loop Through Concepts').item.json.total_duration_seconds }}seconds

---

## CREATOMATE EFFECTS LIBRARY
Use ONLY these exact IDs when specifying effects:

### AVAILABLE LAYOUTS
{{ JSON.stringify($('Creatomate Effects Library').item.json.layouts, null, 2) }}

